<p>The Japan Sports Association cooperates with affiliation groups, 
conducting classes to train sports instructors, and certifying qualifications of 
individuals who meet uniform standards as authorized sports leaders.
Authorized sports instructors make use of knowledge about sports 
medicine and science, teaching "safe, correct, fun sports" that conform to 
criteria such as age, gender, skill level, etc., acting to convey "the essential 
fun and splendor of sports."
